{
  "stem": "1029.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they told us to get moving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we picked up all our belongings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Naturally, my mother fitted me out with two winter coats, you know, put two winter coats on me, you know, because she figured that who knows what may happen?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, she had some forebodings, and people were talking, you know, so we thought, you know, it may not come to a good end.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so then she gathered her things together and put everything in those big valises, and we tied them up with cords and stuff.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we just got moving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was just a long line going through the village.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were no lights.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah. the entire ghetto was moved to the rail station.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the whole town was blacked out, you know, because of the planes and the air raids and so on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And but we could feel the eyes of the-- of the Christians, you know, watching us from behind darkened windows.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we are moving, and some of them rapped on the window a little bit because we were close.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, we were just that yay far away from-- because it's small streets in a village.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We don't know, but I think some of them were happy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of them, you know, they couldn't do anything because if they would have done something, they would've-- they would've-- the same fate would have befallen them as had befallen us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So but most of them were probably happy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were already figuring out what to do, you know, how to take away, you know, our possessions and how to-- how to see what they can do.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
